post.description:
Submits an in-progress worker goal event specified by the Workday ID (WID). This operation is equivalent to submitting a worker goal event in the Manage Goals task.

To add a comment, specify this request body:
{
    "businessProcessParameters": {
        "action":{
            "id": "d9e4223e446c11de98360015c5e6daf6"
        },
         "comment": "Test comment."
    }
}

<b>Secured by:</b> Manage \~Goals\~ (REST Service)

<b>Scope:</b> Performance Enablement
